INSERT INTO `tag_essay` VALUES(13, 2, 11, 1, '\n"Some people prefer to live in a small town, Others prefer to live in a big city. Which place would you prefer to live in? Use specific reasons and details to support your answer. \n\n"', '"   I had lived in a small town until in high school, after that, I has lived in a big city. So I could experience all advantages and disadvantage of a small town and a big city. When I was in a small town, I thouht a small town was better that a big ciry, but after I moved to a large city, I never imagine that I return a tiny community. \n   \n     Initially, in a large city, people could have many cultural opportunities more easily. For example, a few weeks ago, I and my friend living in a small town far from a large city went to the theater to watch very famous musical, ''Cats''. In my case, it took me about half of an hour to go to the theater by subway, but my friend spent almost 3 hours arriving in the theater by car because she lived in a tiny community. She exhausted valuable time in which she did something different and more money so that she drove a car operated with oil. In her small town, there were no theater for musical or play and many of the town were not interested them. So all she could do was that she went to a large city for seeing musical or play. If she had have born in a big community, she could have enjoyed musical and play as much as she wanted. \n\n     Next, much more medicine service is given to people living in a large city. Now I can imagine one documentary televised on TV last year. On documentary a story of one men preparing ''Disabled Olympic'' was introduced. The men had blindness of one eye. According to his words, it originated from a unexpected accident. When he was a child, he and his friend played the game using a toy sword. The game was very exciting and they more and more fell into it. While they enjoying the game, the accident succenly occured. The sword of his friend stung his right eye deeply. He felt a extreme pain on his eye, and cried loudly. No sooner took him to the hospital in town than his mother saw his hurtten eye but doctor said that he should go to the bigger hospital in a big city. So He and his mother went to the hospital in a big city as soon as possible, but he lost his eyesight during going to there. Through this case, we can know why people prefer to live in a big city. \n\n     In conclusion, I prefer to live in a big city that living in a small town. Of course, living in a small town has the advantages ; clean air, pure water and stablility  earned from living with nature. However, when considering that I am young and health also now I need the advantages of cultural chances and medicine servise, it is obviousely much better for me that I live in a large city. "', 'I had<strike> lived in a small town until in high school, after that, I has lived in a big city. So I could experience all advantages and disadvantage of a small town and a big city. When I was in a small town, I t</strike>houht a small town was better that a big ciry, but after I moved to a large city, I never imagine that I return a tiny community. <br>   <br>     Initially, in a large city, people could have many cultural opportunities more easily. For example, a few weeks ago, I and my friend living in a small town far from a large city went to the theater to watch very famous musical, ''Cats''. In my case, it took me about half of an hour to go to the theater by subway, but my friend spent almost 3 hours arriving in the theater by car because she lived in a tiny community. She exhausted valuable time in which she did something different and more money so that she drove a car operated with oil. In her small town, there were no theater for musical or play and many of the town were not interested them. So all she could do was that she went to a large city for seeing musical or play. If she had have born in a big community, she could have enjoyed musical and play as much