INSERT INTO `tag_essay` VALUES(14, 2, 12, 1, '\nPeople attend college or university for many different reasons. Why do you think people attend college or university?', '"   These days, more and more people have been attending University or college. Some are attending University without certain purpose and just follow people around them, while others enter college to prepare their jobs or to study deeply. I think people attending University because they want to have more profound knowledges about their careers and enhance the levels of their cultures. \n         \n               First of all, University helps students to be competent worker by studying their major. There are lots of faculty who have been studying specially and rendering remarkable achievement to their fields. By taking their classes, students learn professors'' accumulated knowledges and wisdom. Also, friends in same major can share informations about goals that they want to achieve in the future. In short, students can develope themselves as a good worker through studying in advanced classes of their major with students who have common interests and goals. \n        In addition, University helps students get common senses and develope sociabilities which are essential to become cultured men. There are many club activities which are helpful to develope ourselves. In my case, I attained intellectual cultures by doing newspaper club activity and became sociable by getting along with various kind of people in the club. Plus, central library in University has many books about liberal arts  available for students who have difficulties in buying expensive books. Shortly, people can cultivate themselves better by attending University.           \n               \n             To sum up, in my opinion, people want to enter University for career preparation and being well-grounded men in various fields. As the society become more complex, university will perform important role of making professional worker and cultivate people. "', 'These days, more and more people have been attending University or college. Some are attending University without certain purpose and just follow people around them, while others enter college to prepare their jobs or to study deeply. I think people attending University because they want to have more profound knowledges about their careers and enhance the levels of their cultures. <br>         <br>               First of all, University helps students to be competent worker by studying their major. There are lots of faculty who have been studying specially and rendering remarkable achievement to their fields. By taking their classes, students learn professors'' accumulated knowledges and wisdom. Also, friends in same major can share informations about goals that they want to achieve in the future. In short, students can develope themselves as a good worker through studying in advanced classes of their major with students who have common interests and goals. <br>        In addition, University helps students get common senses and develope sociabilities which are essential to become cultured men. There are many club activities which are helpful to develope ourselves. In my case, I attained intellectual cultures by doing newspaper club activity and became sociable by getting along with various kind of people in the club. Plus, central library in University has many books about liberal arts  available for students who have difficulties in buying expensive books. Shortly, people can cultivate themselves better by attending University.           <br>               <br>             To sum up, in my opinion, people want to enter University for career preparation and being well-grounded men in various fields. As the society become more complex, university will perform important role of making professional worker and cultivate people.', 'These days, more and more people have been attending University or college. Some are attending University without c