INSERT INTO `tag_essay` VALUES(20, 2, 18, 1, '\nSome people believe that students should be given one long vacation each year. Others believe that students should have several short vacations throughout the year. Which viewpoint do you agree with?', '" The vacation is the opportunity for students to do something special they cannot experience in school. It is important to determine how long the vacation is more efficient for student to relax enough and prepare the next term and to learn the real life from parents and the real society behind school. I believe that long vacation each year can be more helpful for the student than several short vacations throughout the year. \n\n     First, they can do something sufficiently they cannot do during the school time when they have long vacation like learning sports or traveling. When I was freshman in university, I desired to travel European country with back and went around the country with great satisfaction during 2 months summer vacation. If there were only 1 month vacation, I may have not traveled fully and have regretted the lack of time. \n\n    Second, they can be taught from their parents during vacation, and the home education is as important as the school education. When the students have enough long vacation, they can spend more time with their parents besides their other activity. When I was high school student, I helped my mother’s house choirs and my father’s work during winter vacation for 3 months. Before that time, I thought that I was deserved to be taken care of by my parents. But, though the experience, I felt really how difficult was my parents working, and I realized truly I had to respect my parents. It was through my real experience in home that I recognized sincerely respecting my parents. Eventhough I always learned from the teacher that I had to have regard in high my parents. \n\n    In addition, it is necessary for the students to prepare the next term. If they have only short vacation, they cannot have enough time to learn the real experience which cannot be taught from the school and relax at the same time. During vacation, they have to have the time not only doing something they would like to do but relaxing to prepare the next term. If there is only short vacation, they will be too busy to finish the vacation good and get ready the new school semester. \n\n     In conclusion, I am firmly convinced that the long term vacation is essential each year for the students to try what they would like to do which they cannot do during the term and have the opportunity to be trained at home. In addition, through the long vacation, they can complete the vacation well and plan the next term.       "', '', '', '', '', 1, 1, 'essay', 'Tagging', 0, 0, '2013-12-13 13:14:51', '2013-12-21 13:25:33');
