INSERT INTO `tag_essay` VALUES(23, 2, 21, 1, '\n Do you agree or disagree with the following statement? Parents are the best teachers. Use specific reasons and examples to support your answer.', '" There are a wide range of controversies about this statement that parents are the best teacher. Some people think that parents are the best teacher because they give their children many wisdoms of living which they experienced, and they well know their children any other in the world. Others say that parents do not become the best teacher for their children because they really love their children so they can not realize their mistakes, and they are not expert in all fields. However, I disagree that parents are the best teacher. \n\n  First, parents do not point out their children’s mistakes because they have love and attachment for them. They do not see their children with objective views, so they find their children’s mistakes as well as correct their faults. When I ate with my family, children run around the restaurant and made a noise as if it is their house. Although the children’s behaviors had bad influences on other people, their parents do not scold them and angry to people who scold their children. \n\n  Second, parents are not the best teacher because their knowledge does not cover all fields. Although they have various experiences and wisdom for living, they lack expert knowledge on diverse areas such as art, science, and history. Therefore, they could give their children an erroneous knowledge or information, so it may have negative effects on them. If your children ask you what you do not know, you can not give them the right answer. Consequently, your children are disappointed with you, and you might lose your authority as parents. \n\n  In conclusion, it is fact that parents play an important role in their children’s life. However, they are related their children so closely that they overlook their mistakes or faults. Although parents give us much love and consideration, I disagree with this statement for the reasons I have mentioned above.     "', '', '', '', '{"ibc":"2","thesis":"3","topic":"","coherence":"","transition":"","mi":"","si":"","style":"","usage":""}', 1, 0, 'essay', 'Tagging', 0, 0, '2013-12-13 13:14:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
