INSERT INTO `tag_essay` VALUES(731, 3, 1179, 2, '\nDo you agree or disagree with the following statement? Children should be required to help with household tasks as soon as they are able to do so. Use specific reasons and examples to support your answer.', '"In the past in Korea, children were valuable workers. Therefore, parents had the tendency to have more children. In the course of time, However, parents had fewer kids than before and seemed to cherish them. That is to say, children were hardly expected to become a energy source. However, if kids did not help household chores, they would not lose the important factors such as the relation and respect.\n\nFirst of all, household things need conversation. It means that the relation between family members could be better than before through talking about each other. For example, my father was always a being hard to say something related with family affairs. But, as time has passed, I had the chance to settle this chilly relationship through having a dialogue from simple to complex. Now, I have the good relationship with my father. If I did not assist household matters, it would be impossible for me to recover this situation.\n\nNext, housing chores such as doing a laundry and dishes are not simple. However, If I did not directly practice them, it would be impossible for me to know how complex they are and what kinds of knowhow I need to settle the problem. Although they do not appear complex, they have a procedure and method. Only parents know this kinds of the procedure and method. As learning them, I came to respect our parents again.\n\nTo make a story to short, as a coin has two side, there are pros and cons about bring children to clean house chores. Although, now it is not in the past, other sorts of mediums make us to earn important components including relationship between family members and respect for their parents. If I did not choice them, I would maybe earn merit; good relationship and reverence."', '