INSERT INTO `tag_essay` VALUES(739, 3, 1187, 2, '\nSome people prefer to spend their free time outdoors. Other people prefer to spend their leisure time indoors. Would you prefer to be outside or would you prefer to be inside for your leisure activities? Use specific reasons and examples to explain your choice.', '"It is true that society has been developed a lot in so many areas, such as education, environment, and entertainment. This advancement has brought us opportunities to enjoy ourselves indoors. Actually more than two-thirds of people in my country spend leisure time indoors, usually doing computer games. I, However, do not think that spending free time inside is mroe favorable than doing it outside, with regard to more benefits it can bring to us.\n\nFirst of all, people can make friends more easily when they do sport.  It is an absolutely good way to get on well with other people through sport. Moreover, doing sport can improve our health, even though it needs physical efforts. People do not have to consider their health seriously which is becoming a great issue in society.\n\n All people who own their company also has to spend their time outdoors. They are supposed to have the leadership which is a really important skill to run their companies. By means of doing sport, they can make the leadership stronger than ever. Therefore, even if their companies are put into a difficult situation, they can get over it with the strong leadership.\n\nHowever, some people believe that it is also a good way to spend their free time playing computer games without any distractions. I, Nevertheless, do not assert this statement. They become isolated although they do not realize it, and as a result they can probably loss their social skills.\n\nFor these reasons, I can say that I prefer to spend my free time outdoors without hesitation, and I strongly believe that people should spend their time outdoors as there are definitely more benefits and nobody should be isolated fro