INSERT INTO `tag_essay` VALUES(740, 3, 1188, 2, '\nWhat is the most important animal in your country? Why is the animal important? Use reasons and specific details to explain your answer.', '"It is widely accepted that the most important animal is a dog in my country. The following essay explains why I think a dog is the most improtant animal.\n\nTo start with, a dog is more familiar with human beings than any other animal. It is really a crucial point to my country which has become a industrial country. People living in a complex country usually feel lonely, so they tend to find something enough to make them joyful. I believe that a dog is really suitable for it, as a result more than one-thirds of people in my country have dogs, especially in a complex city.\n\n Another point to bear in mind is that a dog can prevent my house from robbery. Actually, there are some reports about these cases. Therefore, when an owner has a dog, the owner can pay less attention for the house while the owner is out of the house, because of the dog which is always attentive. Moreover, having a dog can be educational for children. Due to the lack of friendship with other children, children might not learn social skills. Even though a dog is not a human beings, it might be helpful for children to get along with other pepple.\n\nFor these reasons, I firmly believe that a dog is the most important animal as having it can obstruct people from feeling lonely and it can keep a house safely."', '"It is widely accepted that the most important animal is a dog in my country. The following essay explains why I think a dog is the most improtant animal.<br><br>To start with, a dog is more familiar with human beings than any other animal. It is really a crucial point to my country which has become a industrial country. People living in a complex country usually feel lonely, so they tend to find something enough to make them joyful. I believe that a dog is really suitable for it, as a result more than