INSERT INTO `tag_essay` VALUES(782, 3, 1230, 2, '\n"Do you agree or disagree with the following statement? \nModern technology is creating is a single world culture. Use specific reasons and examples to support your opinion."', '"The world is heading for the unified community along with globalization. This phenomenon is specified as a single world culture. Modern technology has enabled us to bring about it. \n\nFirst, the development of the communication media has brought common experiences for the world. All the people of the world can contact anyone at any time through the Internet. The world-cup games are projected simultaneously all over the world by the media satellites. The communication technology advancements take us to a similar culture. \n\nSecondly, it is more available for us to travel evrywhere of the world due to the innovations of of transportation. Within 24 hours we can go to the opposite sites of the earth. The mass flow of the global people cause this planet to have the familiar experience, which becomes the basis for the single world culture. \n\nFinally, the evolution process of the world''s countries has traced the general path ac the capitalism has been spread all over the world. All teenagers of the world, except a very few naton, would enjoy the Mcdonald hamburgers and Coca-cokes. Capitalism accompanied by the liberalism would provide the unilateral cultural history. \n\nThe rapid development of communication and transportation in the wide rooted capitalism have another featurre of the worldwide culture. This trends would be more accelerated om the perspective that the culture is the coomon and accumulated recognition of a community."', '"The world is heading for the unified community along with globalization. This phenomenon is specified as a single world culture. Modern technology has enabled us to bring about it. <br><br>First, the development of the communication media has brought common experiences for the world. All the people of the w