INSERT INTO `tag_essay` VALUES(787, 3, 1235, 2, '\n"In general, people are living longer now. Discuss the causes of this phenomenon. Use specific reasons and details to develop your essay."', '"These days, there are a lot of old people in our society. Sometimes, the aging of the people in a society causes problems like the difficulty in an employment, and the isolation of old people. Why are people living longer now? Although there are lots of reasons, I think the development of medical technology and the increase in exercise time are main causes. \n\nTo begin with, because of the development of medical technology, people can be healed in hospitals. Since the birth of human beings, people always want to live longer, so it makes many improvements in the medical and drug realms. Today, by go to hospitals, we can easily find the disease we have, and it is possible to treat most of diseases. Like this, the development of medical treatment allows humans to live longer. \n\nMoreover, according to the improvement of life quality, people could spend time on entertainments such sports as hiking, swimming, soccer, jogging, so it has a good effect on human health.', '"These days, there are a lot of old people in our society. Sometimes, the aging of the people in a society causes problems like the difficulty in an employment, and the isolation of old people. Why are people living longer now? Although there are lots of reasons, I think the development of medical technology and the increase in exercise time are main causes. <br><br>To begin with, because of the development of medical technology, people can be healed in hospitals. Since the birth of human beings, people always want to live longer, so it makes many improvements in the medical and drug realms. Today, by go to hospitals, we can easily find the disease we have, and it is possible to treat most of diseases. Like this, the development of medical treatment allows humans to live longer. <br><br>Moreover, according to the improvement of life quality, people could spend time on entertainments such sports as hiking, swimming, soccer, jogging, so it has a good effect on human health.', '"<span class=''in'' tag=''IN''>&lt;IN&gt;These days, there are a lot of old people in our society. Sometimes, the aging of the people in a society causes problems like the difficulty in an employment, and the isolation of old people. <span class=''ts'' tag=''TS''>&lt;TS&gt;Why are people living longer now? Although there are lots of reasons, I think the development of medical technology and the increase in exercise time are main causes.&lt;/TS&gt;</span>&lt;/IN&gt;</span> \n\n<span class=''bo'' tag=''BO1''>&lt;BO1&gt;<span class=''mi'' tag=''MI1''>&lt;MI1&gt;<span class=''tr'' tag=''TR''>&lt;TR&gt;To begin with&lt;/TR&gt;</span>, because of the development of medical technology, people can be healed in hospitals.&lt;/MI1&gt;</span> <span class=''si'' tag=''SI1''>&lt;SI1&gt;Since the birth of human beings, people always want to live longer, so it makes many improvements in the medical and drug realms. <span class=''tr'' tag=''TR''>&lt;TR&gt;Today&lt;/TR&gt;</span>, by go to hospitals, we can easily find the disease we have, and it is possible to treat most of diseases. <span class=''tr'' tag=''TR''>&lt;TR&gt;Like this&lt;/TR&gt;</span>, the development of medical treatment allows humans to live longer.&lt;/SI1&gt;</span>&lt;/BO1&gt;</span> \n\n<span class=''bo'' tag=''BO2''>&lt;BO2&gt;<span class=''mi'' tag=''MI2''>&lt;MI2&gt;<span class=''tr'' tag=''TR''>&lt;TR&gt;Moreover&lt;/TR&gt;</span>, according to the improvement of life quality, people could spend time on entertainments such sports as hiking, swimming, soccer, jogging, so it has a good effect on human health.&lt;/MI2&gt;</span> <span class=''si'' tag=''SI2''>&lt;SI2&gt;<TRActually&lt;/TR&gt;</span>, there are numerous people enjoy body building, swimming, or jogging after studies, or works. <span class=''ex'' tag=''EX''>&lt;EX&gt;<span class=''tr'' tag=''TR''>&lt;TR&gt;From my experience&lt;/TR&gt;</span>, I often go to sports center in the evening in order to make the body healthy. Even though I have gone to the health convenience for 2 months, I can feel better.&lt;/EX&gt;</span>&lt;/SI2&gt;</span>&lt;/BO2&gt;</span> \n\n<span class=''co'' tag=''CO''>&lt;CO&gt;<span class=''tr'' tag=''TR''>&lt;TR&gt;To sum up&lt;/TR&gt;</span>, as mentioned above, there are many causes which make people live longer, and I think the development of medical technology and the investment in exercise are the most important reasons that affect on human life spans.&lt;/CO&gt;</span>"', 'This is a pretty good essay, but I think you need to add more support to your argument. You could definitely add more examples and statistics. You say a lot of studies have been done on the effect of exercise? Ok, cite one. Don''t make the reader take your word for it. Finally, take out one of the transitions in your conclusion. You don''t need two.', '{"ibc":"5","thesis":"5","topic":"5","coherence":"4","transition":"4","mi":"5","si":"3","style":"4","usage":"4"}', 1, 0, 'essay', 'Tagging', 0, 0, '2013-12-20 23:49:06', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
INSERT INTO `tag_essay` VALUES(788, 3, 1236, 2, '\n Some people prefer to spend time with one or two close friends. Others choose to spend time with a large number of friends. Compare the advantages of each choice. Which of these two ways of spending time do you prefer? Use specific reasons to support your answer.', '"', '"', '"<span class=''in'' tag=''IN''>&lt;IN&gt;<Through our life, friends are taking an important role. <span class=''ts'' tag=''TS''>&lt;TS&gt;Given the choice, some people prefer to spend time with a few close friends, while others prefer to spend most of their time with a lot of friends. <span class=''tr'' tag=''TR''>&lt;TR&gt;Undoubtedly&lt;/TR&gt;</span>, both aspects are advantageous. <span class=''tr'' tag=''TR''>&lt;TR&gt;Nonetheless&lt;/TR&gt;</span>, as I will demonstrate through several definite examples, spending time with a large number of friends are more advantageous.&lt;/TS&gt;</span>&lt;/IN&gt;</span> \n\n<span class=''bo'' tag=''BO1''>&lt;BO1&gt;<span class=''mi'' tag=''MI1''>&lt;MI1&gt;<span class=''tr'' tag=''TR''>&lt;TR&gt;On the one hand&lt;/TR&gt;</span>, getting together with a few friends has several benefits.&lt;/MI1&gt;</span> <span class=''si'' tag=''SI1''>&lt;SI1&gt;<span class=''tr'' tag=''TR''>&lt;TR&gt;To begin with&lt;/TR&gt;</span>, it is easy to keep the secret with one or two close friends. <span class=''tr'' tag=''TR''>&lt;TR&gt;Generally&lt;/TR&gt;</span>, the secret tends to be easily broken if many people are involved in the secret. <span class=''tr'' tag=''TR''>&lt;TR&gt;Besides&lt;/TR&gt;</span>, a few close friends are better when someone is in a difficult situation. There is a Korean saying that one true friend is as much worth as one hundred friends. <span class=''ex'' tag=''EX''>&lt;EX&gt;<span class=''tr'' tag=''TR''>&lt;TR&gt;From my personal experience&lt;/TR&gt;</span>, I felt there was only one close friend who really cared for me when I got stuck in a trouble.&lt;/EX&gt;</span> <span class=''tr'' tag=''TR''>&lt;TR&gt;Furthermore&lt;/TR&gt;</span>, when it comes to making a decision, their opinions are seldom scattered. <span class=''ex'' tag=''EX''>&lt;EX&gt;I used to go to movies on Saturday night with one of my close friends. There was no conflict between us. Even if our opinions are quite different, we made a decision in a short manner.&lt;/EX&gt;</span></SI1&lt;/BO1&gt;</span> \n\n<span class=''bo'' tag=''BO2''>&lt;BO2&gt;<span class=''mi'' tag=''MI2''>&lt;MI2&gt;<span class=''tr'' tag=''TR''>&lt;TR&gt;On the other hand&lt;/TR&gt;</span>, spending time with a large number of friends give us a lot of advantages.&lt;/MI2&gt;</span> <span class=''si'' tag=''SI2''>&lt;SI2&gt;It enables us to share a variety of background and experience. <span class=''tr'' tag=''TR''>&lt;TR&gt;Generally&lt;/TR&gt;</span>, most people have their own backgrounds and experiences, which are different from each other. <span class=''tr'' tag=''TR''>&lt;TR&gt;On top of that&lt;/TR&gt;</span>, each person has a different opinion on the same matters. We can experience different perspectives with a variety of friends. <TRBesides&lt;/TR&gt;</span>, some sports needs more than 2 people, such as basketball, soccer, and so on. It is possible to enjoy these kinds of sports and group activities with a large number of friends. <span class=''ex'' tag=''EX''>&lt;EX&gt;<span class=''tr'' tag=''TR''>&lt;TR&gt;Moreover&lt;/TR&gt;</span>, there is a general Korean saying that happiness is increasing twice and sadness is lessening half when more people are involved.&lt;/EX&gt;</span> It is true because humans are social animals so that their feelings are added and lessened when more people are being together.&lt;/SI2&gt;</span>&lt;/BO2&gt;</span> \n\n<span class=''co'' tag=''CO''>&lt;CO&gt;<span class=''tr'' tag=''TR''>&lt;TR&gt;To sum up&lt;/TR&gt;</span>, it is advantageous to hang around with a few close friends in terms of secrecy, true friends and quick decision; <span class=''tr'' tag=''TR''>&lt;TR&gt;however&lt;/TR&gt;</span> spending time with a large number of friends is more advantageous in terms of sharing experience, playing sports and the Korean saying. <span class=''tr'' tag=''TR''>&lt;TR&gt;Therefore&lt;/TR&gt;</span> I prefer to spend most of my time with many friends.&lt;/CO&gt;</span>"', 'This essay is pretty good, but I think you need to explain your examples a little more, especially in your first main body paragraph. Also, you are in danger of using too many transitions. Start by taking the transition out of your thesis statement to make it stronger.', '{"ibc":"5","thesis":"4","topic":"5","coherence":"4","transition":"4","mi":"5","si":"4","style":"4","usage":"4"}', 1, 0, 'essay', 'Tagging', 0, 0, '2013-12-20 23:49:06', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
INSERT INTO `tag_essay` VALUES(789, 3, 1237, 2, '\nSome people prefer to get up early in the morning and start the days work. Others prefer to get up later in the day and work until late at night. Which do you prefer? Use specific reasons and examples to support your choice.', '"I actually support people to get up early and to work at the days for various reason. I consider that the health, The pattern of life are reasons for my supporting. Although some people might think that nocturnal working need sometimes for some people but it is their own thinking not for everyone. \n\nFirstly. The health are most important for all people. The methods of keeping the health are various. I think that foundation of them is to be people to get up early and to work at days. When people gets up at early morning, they can have more light head feelings then it helps people working more effectively than nocturnal working. \n\nSecondly. Our bodies are made for acting at days and for sleeping, taking a break at night. If people act at night in contrast of our bodies pattern, this will give people bad condition for spoiling body pattern. For examples, I experienced this situation at my university vacation. Because I woke up approximately at 1~2 pm, can not sleep well at night. I spended my plying computers at night and reading the books. After the half of a month, I had a little headache and ennui. \n\nTo sum up, people who get up early and work at the days having literally good habitation. They are more activating, and have good condition to work, play."', '"I actually support people to get up early and to work at the days for various reason. I consider that the health, The pattern of life are reasons for my supporting. Although some people might think that nocturnal working need sometimes for some people but it is their own thinking not for everyone. <br><br>Firstly. The health are most important for all people. The methods of keeping the health are various. I think that foundation of 