INSERT INTO `tag_essay` VALUES(791, 3, 1239, 2, '\nYou have the opportunity to visit a foreign country for two weeks. Which country would you like to visit? Use specific reasons and details to explain your choice.', '"Visiting another country is a common thing in these days. Many people desire to have a chance to visit a foreign country because it gives them unfogettable memory in their life. In my case, I want to visit Canada for two reasons; first, I want to feel comfortable and imagine how the novelist wrote ''Anne of Green Gables'' in Prince Edward Island where is the back-ground of the novel. Second, I could see the Niagara Falls in Canada and learn greatness of the nature.\n\nBeing the back-ground of the novel, ''Anne of Green Gables'', Prince Edward Island may be picturesque place, and I can feel comfortable and imagine how the novelist''s life goes on. Since I am crazy about the work, it would be never forgotten if I have the chance to visit Canada. I think two weeks are enough time for going around the place, and imagining life of the novelist. In this respect, I want to visit Canada, especially Prince Edward Island. \n\nIn addition, Niagara Falls in Canada is the reason why I want to visit Canada, because I could feel immense of the nature through seeing Niagara Falls. I have heard that Niagara Falls is the senicest falls in the world. Moreover, everyone who sees Niagara Falls surprises of its magnitude. I think visiting Canada to see Niagara Falls is more worth for me than visiting other countries in that it could teach me how the nature majestic is. I believe that the experience would be good for me for sure, since I have not felt the greatness of the nature in small country, where I am living now, Korea. \n\nTo sum up, if I had the opportunity to visit another country for two weeks, then I would go Canada because I could be moderate in Prince Edward Island, Canada, which was the back-ground of the novel I have mentioned as well as make an illusion about